# GapRoll — Agent Rules (Single Source of Truth)
# This file is symlinked to CLAUDE.md — edit only .cursorrules

## Stack
- Frontend: Next.js 15 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Shadcn/UI
- Backend: FastAPI (Python 3.12), Supabase (PostgreSQL + RLS)
- Agents: LangGraph (deterministic, HITL breakpoints)
- Hosting: Hetzner + Coolify

## Hard Rules
- ALWAYS use Tailwind CSS for styling. NEVER use .module.css or external CSS libraries.
- API endpoints in Next.js: ALWAYS use app/api/ Route Handlers (route.ts)
- Database: ALWAYS use Supabase client from @supabase/ssr for server-side auth
- Payments: Fakturownia.pl + Przelewy24 (NEVER Stripe)
- State management: Zustand (NEVER Redux)

## Currency Formatting
- ALWAYS use Intl.NumberFormat for PLN: new Intl.NumberFormat('pl-PL', { style: 'currency', currency: 'PLN' }).format(value)
- NEVER concatenate 'zł' or 'PLN' as strings
- Database: store amounts in GROSZE (integer), convert to PLN only in UI layer

## Banned Technologies
- AWS, Azure, GCP → Hetzner
- CrewAI, AutoGen → LangGraph
- MongoDB, Firebase → Supabase PostgreSQL
- Material UI, Chakra → Shadcn/UI
- Stripe → Fakturownia.pl + Przelewy24
- Vercel → Hetzner + Coolify

## Persona (Grażyna Test)
- Target: Polish HR manager, 45-55, conservative
- Language: Formal Polish, NO English jargon in UI
- Use: "Luka płacowa", "Wartościowanie stanowisk", "Raport zgodności"
- NEVER use: "Dashboard insights", "AI Agent", "Churn"

## Compliance
- EU Directive 2023/970 (Pay Transparency)
- Every metric must have legal citation (Art. X)
- RODO/GDPR: PII protection, audit logs, Row Level Security
- EU AI Act Art. 14: HITL approval for all high-risk decisions
